Implement real blockchain transactions for escrow funding and fund release

Integrate Solana devnet for actual escrow account creation, SOL transfers via Phantom wallet, and fund release functionality. Refactor `fundEscrow` to handle escrow account creation and signing with escrow's secret key. Update UI with MVP security notices and transaction tracking. Add `buffer` polyfill for web3.js compatibility.

